{"ID":"20260305082130-ftfamug","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-ftfamug","title":"变量模版","type":"doc","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-vyor9ao","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-vyor9ao","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"变量模板"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-l2aa0ig","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-l2aa0ig","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"变量模版是 C++14 引入的一个特性，它允许你定义一个变量，这个变量本身是参数化的（即它的类型或值可以根据模板参数而变化）。"},{"Type":"NodeHardBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在此之前，只有函数和类可以被模板化。变量模板扩展了模板的适用范围。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-u000orq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-u000orq","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"语法"},{"Type":"NodeHardBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\u2029```C++"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\u2029template \u003ctypename T\u003e"},{"Type":"NodeHardBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"T variable_name = initial_value;"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-y72yzj7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-y72yzj7","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"// 或者带有非类型模板参数"},{"Type":"NodeHardBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"template \u003cint N\u003e"},{"Type":"NodeHardBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"int array_size = N;"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-xyixxlz","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-xyixxlz","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"\n**作用和优点**  \n1. 类型依赖的常量： 定义一个常量，其类型或值取决于模板参数；\n2. 泛型配置： 提供泛型的配置值或默认值；\n3. 简化代码： 避免为不同类型重复定义相似的常量或变量。  \n\n**示例** \n```C++\n\u2029#include \u003ciostream\u003e  \n#include \u003cstring\u003e  \n  \n// 1. 定义一个变量模板：pi 的类型取决于模板参数 T  \ntemplate \u003ctypename T\u003e  \nconstexpr T pi = T(3.1415926535897932385L);  \n  \n// 2. 定义一个变量模板：用于获取容器的默认容量  \ntemplate \u003ctypename Container\u003e  \nconstexpr size_t default_capacity = 10;  \n  \n// 3. 定义一个变量模板：用于获取数组的默认值  \ntemplate \u003ctypename T\u003e  \nT default_value = T(); // 默认构造  \n  \nint main() {  \n// 使用 pi 变量模板  \nstd::cout.precision(10);  \nstd::cout \u003c\u003c \"pi\u003cdouble\u003e: \" \u003c\u003c pi\u003cdouble\u003e \u003c\u003c std::endl;  \nstd::cout \u003c\u003c \"pi\u003cfloat\u003e: \" \u003c\u003c pi\u003cfloat\u003e \u003c\u003c std::endl;  \nstd::cout \u003c\u003c \"pi\u003clong double\u003e: \" \u003c\u003c pi\u003clong double\u003e \u003c\u003c std::endl;  \n  \n// 使用 default_capacity 变量模板  \nstd::cout \u003c\u003c \"default_capacity\u003cstd::vector\u003cint\u003e\u003e: \" \u003c\u003c default_capacity\u003cstd::vector\u003cint\u003e\u003e \u003c\u003c std::endl;  \nstd::cout \u003c\u003c \"default_capacity\u003cstd::string\u003e: \" \u003c\u003c default_capacity\u003cstd::string\u003e \u003c\u003c std::endl;  \n  \n// 使用 default_value 变量模板  \nint int_default = default_value\u003cint\u003e;  \nstd::string string_default = default_value\u003cstd::string\u003e;  \nstd::cout \u003c\u003c \"default_value\u003cint\u003e: \" \u003c\u003c int_default \u003c\u003c std::endl;  \nstd::cout \u003c\u003c \"default_value\u003cstd::string\u003e: '\" \u003c\u003c string_default \u003c\u003c \"'\" \u003c\u003c std::endl;  \n  \nreturn 0;  \n}\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]}]}